== Visits hosted in Uzbekistan by Shavkat Mirziyoyev == Since September 2016, all the visits to Uzbekistan have had the character of working visits. Mostly it was giving honor to the First President [[Islam Karimov]] at his burial site. On 16 September 2017, Kazakh President [[Nursultan Nazarbayev]] visited Uzbekistan with state visit. That was the first state visit hosted by Mirziyoyev in Tashkent.<ref>https://www.uzdaily.uz/articles-id-34111.htm</ref>
