{{Infobox song contest | name = Melodifestivalen | year = 1980 | theme = | logo = | final = 8 March 1980 | presenters = [[Bengt Bedrup]] | winner = "[[Just nu!]]" by [[Tomas Ledin]] | vote = Regional juries | host = | venue = [[Sveriges Television|SVT]] Television Centre, [[Stockholm]] | entries = | interval = | opening = }}
'''[[Melodifestivalen]] 1980''' was the selection for the 20th song to represent [[Sweden]] at the [[Eurovision Song Contest]]. It was the 19th time that this system of picking a song had been used. 120 songs were submitted to [[Sveriges Television|SVT]] for the competition. The final was broadcast on [[SVT1|TV1]] but was not broadcast on radio.
